&lt;p&gt;Continence Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a recognised provider of innovative, high quality services &lt;strong&gt;Central London Community Health Trust &lt;/strong&gt;are looking for an exceptional Band 6 Continence Nurse to join our highly respected community nursing team in Merton.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Continence Nurse within the Planned Care team you will be supporting the delivery of safe and effective continence assessments, treatments and care for community patients. You will be supported by our Continence Specialist Nurse and will work closely with community nursing colleagues. Community nursing and continence care experience is required for this role as well as experience in teaching, mentoring and supporting others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have excellent communication/interpersonal skills and would enjoy the challenge of delivering high quality care for patients with continence needs then we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
